data.description: Wonderfully maintained 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home located in the heart of San Antonio. Just Minutes From All Of The Downtown Attractions, The Pearl, The Riverwalk, Hospitals, Shopping, Fine Dining, The Zoo, Brackenridge Park and More!  UPGRADES MADE WITHIN LAST 4 YEARS:   PERMITTED ELECTRICAL WORK DONE, NEW ROOF INSTALLED, NEW ELECTRIC WATER HEATER, NEW HVAC, ENERGY EFFICIENT DOUBLE PANE/ TILT WINDOWS, BACK DECK INSTALLED, STORAGE FOR OUTDOOR SUPPLIES, QUARTZ COUNTER TOPS, HIGH END BACK SPLASH AND CUSTOM CABINETS.
